parameters: Soldier: "Ah! It's Commander Kru!"
Kru: "Hey... You're full of energy, aren't you?"
Soldier: "I'm working hard to become as strong as Commander Kru."
Kru: "Well... you might want to reconsider that."
Soldier: "?"
Soldier: "Ah! This is Kru, the head swordsman!"
Kru: "Hey... you're full of energy, aren't you?"
Soldier: "I'm working hard to become as strong as you, Head Swordsman Kru."
Kru: "Well... maybe you should give it up."
Soldier: "?"
Soldier "Haa haa haa..."
Soldier: "Ahh, I don't want to go on a mission."
Kru: "Me neither."
Soldier: "Well, well, as busy as ever, I see."
Soldier: "Ahh, I'm tired."
Soldier: "Ah, thank you."

Soldier: "This is Swordsman Leader Kru. Chancellor Shif-sama is waiting for
you in the audience chamber."
Soldier: "The audience chamber is out of here and on the second floor."
Kru: "Yeah... Thanks for telling me."
Kru: "What is this flesh!"
Kru: "Hah hah... was it... a dream...?"
Kru: "Hm? What was the dream about again... something red..."
Kru: "Red... flesh?"
Soldier: "Have you awakened, Captain Kru of the Swordsmen?"
Kru: "Ah, good morning."
Soldier: "You seemed to be having quite a restless sleep, are you alright?"
Kru: "Ah, thank you. I'm fine."
Soldier: "Chancellor Shif is waiting for you in the audience chamber."
Kru: "Understood, I'll go right away."
